{"tid":1892543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指東區醫院76歲、80歲女士確診　均曾到北角「福慧精舍」　成佛堂第4宗個案　","createTime":"2020-02-22T15:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T15:16:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e086a51d7d5974ba0f17dff07650d13d1acfb15d","tid":1892543,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fokwai-08-08-08_FxrjA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffokwai-08-08-08_FxrjA_1200x0.png&h=e77c1b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢新型冠狀病毒在香港持續傳播，有公立醫院醫護人員向《立場新聞》透露，一名 76 歲女士確診，在東區醫院留醫，病人報稱曾到位於北角的福慧精舍；另有一名80歲女士亦確診，亦報稱曾到同一佛堂。若個案最終證實確診，確診個案將累計至71宗，亦是第 4 宗曾到福慧精舍的病人。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署今日表示，一名 96 歲女性確診，病人 1 月底曾到位於北角的福慧精舍。另外，根據署方資料，第 65 宗個案的 70 歲女病人亦曾前往同一間佛堂。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君指，由於該佛堂已經關閉，暫時仍在尋求負責人，但得悉女病人當日長時間在佛堂內，當時約有 20 至 30 人參與誦經及其他活動，另外會在另一地方分派食物，但詳細情況未掌握，署方需繼續調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-消息指東區醫院76歲女士確診-曾到北角-福慧精舍-成佛堂第3宗個案/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A276%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92-%E7%A6%8F%E6%85%A7%E7%B2%BE%E8%88%8D-%E6%88%90%E4%BD%9B%E5%A0%82%E7%AC%AC3%E5%AE%97%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%2F&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=3318fdad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A276%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92-%E7%A6%8F%E6%85%A7%E7%B2%BE%E8%88%8D-%E6%88%90%E4%BD%9B%E5%A0%82%E7%AC%AC3%E5%AE%97%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%2F&h=60adcf22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-消息指東區醫院76歲女士確診-曾到北角-福慧精舍-成佛堂第3宗個案/</a>"},{"pid":"8731afe1e567318d1e8f04f58cf63c3b98bc9f7a","tid":1892543,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"26 歲出埋院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a05a5e4928243f925a0e10c89058a870c35996c","tid":1892543,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351ed8e46c6a62eb94df787e647294b5788a74d8","tid":1892543,"uid":44951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"佛系抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967e40dd151c9e2da5d9d7b9b423752701c1791d","tid":1892543,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"80歲，96歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f516275a347d8825635089b79ede6ead5b1404b","tid":1892543,"uid":76341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:11:11.000Z","msg":"平均80歳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ebe412aadd3a025314b797ebd9365d51b644c8","tid":1892543,"uid":281483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"福建幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541fb7bc89a4211e0fc712b74868eec9069a40aa","tid":1892543,"uid":88982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"福建幫 夠鐘出黎領獎啦"}]}